#
# Loads ~/.config/wayland-desktop/config.yaml and provides bidirectional alias
# resolution for desktop names, screen names, and app identifiers.
#
# Resolution is always bidirectional and fall-through:
#   - "Job1"  → "Job 1"   (alias → canonical)
#   - "Job 1" → "Job 1"   (canonical passes through unchanged)
#   - "bogus" → "bogus"   (unknown names pass through; never raises)
#
# The library always works with canonical KWin names internally.
# Aliases are applied at the CLI/user-facing boundary only.
